NUMBERS HAVE REMAINED BASICALLY STABLE SINCE APRIL, WITH 
MECKLENBURG-VORPOMMERN, BRANDENBURG AND SAXONY ACTUALLY 
SHOWING IMPROVEMENT OVER RECENT MONTHS. 
 
